title: Texas teen gunman planned suicide: governor
text:
Texas teen gunman planned suicide: governor Friday, May 18, 2018 - 02:40
Texas Governor Greg Abbott says a male student who entered a Texas high school on Friday and shot dead ten people, including fellow pupils, had planned to end the attack with his suicide but instead surrendered to police. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
